    }

`this.list` is a collection (list, set, or array), and that code assigns `c` to each element of the collection.

So, if `this.list` were a collection {&quot;2S&quot;, &quot;3H&quot;, &quot;4S&quot;} then the `cardString` on the end would be this string:

    2S
    3H
